Victory in Europe (Time-Life World War II Series)
Time-Life Books | 1982 | ISBN 0809434067 | English | 216 pages | PDF | 44.8 MB

May 8th is the anniversary of VE Day (Victory in Europe Day), marking the end of the Second World War in Europe. The book contains range of data to show how the war affected life in Europe, and how the world has changed since then
